      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Available is a 2003 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed with recent bushing refreshes, and critical preventive maintenance\u2014including subframe reinforcement and a VANOS overhaul\u2014has been addressed. Finished in Carbon Black, it offers exceptional lateral kinematics and a linear power band that pulls hard to the 8,000 RPM redline. A mechanically sound, driver-focused machine ready for the apex.",
