      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and care. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though upon close inspection, you will notice a few minor stone chips on the leading edge of the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper from standard use. The interior is exceptionally clean; the leather seats are firm and free of punctures, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s entry bolster. All cabin technology, including the infotainment screen and heated seats, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, and I have the records to prove it. The engine idling is whisper-quiet, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains tight over bumps. The tires were replaced last season and have significant tread remaining. This is a well-maintained, honest car that is ready for its next chapter without any immediate maintenance needs.",
